divs: sighting detailsi watched a red and blue pulsating object move like a hummingbird for about 1\2 an hour. 2 more similiar objects went into the direction of the object. all of them disappeared behind the trees after 1\2 an hour or so. but i was watching mostly just the one pulsating one for at least 1\2 an hour. it seemed to be hovering, but then also moving like a hummingbird at times. sometimes it moved in a figure eight pattern and sometimes in a circular pattern. i definitely have never seen anything like it before. it was not a satellite, plane, helicopter, star, comet, or weather balloon. the sky was completely clear with no clouds and there was no wind. i watched it outside on my deck. it made me feel, of course, incredibly excited, anxious, awestruck
